{"tid":1787590,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"召集IT人 諗到個監察議員嘅方法","createTime":"2019-12-18T04:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T08:40:46.000Z","uid":215811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eabf7d78c1d4ad97fa5ab2a574515ae8d61fffbf","tid":1787590,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"之前都見過手足開post講可以整個 app比選民同區議員互動。<br />\n<br />\n市民方面可提出意見，知到區議員有做啲咩無做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區議員方面可以知道居民需要，四年後亦都係一張靚靚成績表<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會覺得咁用返佢哋FB咪得囉，我唔同意，<br />\n一尼FB的POST太散亂，混集左比較多情緒回覆（例如打氣，鬧）；<br />\n二來難以整理，比較難跟進；<br />\n三來個話語權喺議員方，市民最多係comments, 又係番返去難跟住果度<br />\n<br />\n我心目中嘅構思係類似app嘅回饋網站咁：<br />\n市民/議員有得提出建議，其他人留言upvote做唔做， 如果議員决定做而做緊可以更新status做處理中/己完成，多人問但係做唔到/唔值得做嘅建議，區議員都可以喺下面留言解釋。<br />\n<br />\n類似係咁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://featureupvote.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureupvote.com%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=8c1d87d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://featureupvote.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟唔識寫APP，以上抛磚引玉跪求IT絲巴介入幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93874e372bfcf0b3c67eb6f55c21b1463390819","tid":1787590,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"249b300ca430b6a6d8634d94984c0cdc093b8f77","tid":1787590,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"d1eb2179fd62fd9b65f65592c9ff1f4d0dd741eb","tid":1787590,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"553fc75f473345496166d81c7828036c99828fa6